  "remarks": "Yan Novikov is General Director of JSC Almaz-Antey air and space defence corporation (“Almaz-Antey”). Almaz-Antey is a key company within the Russian military-industrial complex. Companies within the Almaz-Antey holding structure produce various types of defence hardware and equipment in use by the Russian Armed Forces in their war of aggression against Ukraine.",
